HEADWORD: Cushionless
<hw>Cush"ion*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not furnished with a
cushion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Rows of long, <qex>cushionless</qex> benches, supplying the place
